text: Torsten Lennart Back (28 May 1933 – 1 August 2022)Lennart Back död was a Swedish race walker. He won a bronze medal in the 20 km event at the 1958 European Championships. He finished sixth at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Olympians for Sweden
